abstract: Examples disclosed herein relate to a likelihood of success of a remote document service. For example, a processor may determine to transmit information about a remote document service to a device based on a likelihood of success associated with the ability of the device to perform the remote document service. The likelihood of success may be based on the performance history of the device and a factor associated with performance history and likelihood of success

title: Likelihood of Success of a Remote Document Service
